## **ğŸ”§ Quick Reference**

### **For Developers**
```bash
# Create staging release
git tag v1.2.3-rc && git push origin v1.2.3-rc

# Create production release  
git tag v1.2.3 && git push origin v1.2.3
```

### **For Deployment Managers**
1. Check pipeline: [Jenkins Build](https://Lienkinsbuild.intra.corp/jenkins/job/E3/job/CRMX20Bulk%20Loader%20Module/job/backend-build/)
2. Document in Confluence
3. Create JIRA ticket
4. Follow change management deadlines

